reviewText: It was a cute show - the movies (Boris Karloff and Brenden Fraiser) are pretty good. Its quasi-historical and its a whimsical show for youngsters - considering I was 12 when the show came on the air. So, all - in - all its pretty good. Also, the disc was in great condition too. Have all 3 volumes - fantastic.
